{"tid":352731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現避孕套 爭執間怒斬213刀 新移民涉謀殺偷情女友","createTime":"2017-08-09T04:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T05:40:35.000Z","uid":33643,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfcfa1d1ebb240f1112ade51b15e976c83f5599e","tid":352731,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">法庭：怒斬213刀 新移民涉謀殺偷情女友</span><br />\n<br />\n2017年8月9日 上午9:26<br />\n新移民來港的內地男散工在○九年時，因在<span style=\"color: red;\">居所外發現用過的安全套</span>，揭發同居女友另結新歡並曾帶對方回家偷情，二人為此爭執，期間散工涉嫌用菜刀狂斬女友二百一十三刀至死。他之後往內地匿藏，一日後返港時被捕，事後被控一項謀殺罪，案件昨於高院開審。<span style=\"color: green;\">死者的新男友在庭上供稱，事發前一天因他與死者均放假，遂相約在死者家中做愛，之後他把用過的安全套丟棄在大廈梯間的垃圾桶。</span><br />\n<br />\n涉案四十八歲被告梁耀強，報稱散工，被控在○九年九月十二日，於長沙灣青山道和興大廈住所內，謀殺當時卅五歲的女友楊秀瑜。<br />\n<br />\n控方昨在開案詞透露，被告與死者過去都曾在內地結婚，並各自育有一名女兒，二人其後在內地結識並成為情侶，死者先來港居住，被告則在○九年四月聯同死者與前夫生的女兒來港定居，惟被告來港半年後，即懷疑死者另結新歡。<br />\n<br />\n疑兇曾匿內地 返港被捕<br />\n<br />\n其實死者來港後，隨即覓得一份便利店店員工作，並在工作時認識了一名小巴男司機，更迅速發展至有性關係。<br />\n<br />\n案發前一日，死者與小巴司機在死者住所內性交，事後將用過的安全套棄於大廈梯間，遭被告發現「罪證」。被告遂於案發日的凌晨，向死者大興問罪之師，並用刀斬死者。被告在同日下午，約他與前妻所生的女兒見面，並將一筆財物交給女兒，然後被告前赴內地。他在翌日經深圳灣口岸回香港時被捕。被告承認有斬死者，控方向陪審團指出，他們需要決定的是，被告是否有干犯謀殺罪。<br />\n<br />\n死者新歡任職小巴司機<br />\n<br />\n控方之後傳召死者當時的新歡陳北勝作供。<br />\n<br />\n任職小巴司機的陳供稱，他駕駛的小巴路線，站頭附近有一間便利店，因此在○九年八月時，他認識了任店員的死者，短短一個月，兩人發展至有性關係。<br />\n<br />\n案發八年始審 「非不尋常」<br />\n<br />\n案發前一日他和死者剛巧都放假，遂相約在下午時分，於死者住所內幽會，期間二人做愛，至入夜後二人往佐敦共膳，始分道揚鑣。陳表示在性交後，他把安全套丟在大廈梯間的垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n由於本案事發距今已經將近八年，法官昨日為此提醒陪審團，有時法庭審訊未必可以在案件發生後的短時間內進行，此點並沒有不尋常之處。案件今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCC 37/2017<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tzlcOg2o1TVRlMilTJsFtw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTkyO2g9NTU4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/50ea88ebb84517aa11bf5d6e78d11f0e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtzlcOg2o1TVRlMilTJsFtw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9OTkyO2g9NTU4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F50ea88ebb84517aa11bf5d6e78d11f0e&h=6d7007d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMore: From 明報<br />\n<br />\n被告當晚在梯間發現避孕套，翌日質問楊婦，兩人爭執，其間被告走進廚房拿起菜刀亂斬，事主全身中刀213處死亡。<span style=\"color: red;\">被告行兇後曾致電女兒稱「我殺了她（事主）」，「我斬了她很多刀」</span>，之後潛逃內地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ebba2e4d4056d6662c603307e39eb97c2f7633","tid":352731,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00acb9f3a6a8659009d91ce75962ef6db3d0de1","tid":352731,"uid":56432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:11:12.000Z","msg":"大陸喱死就死係大6啦，死都污染香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a82191fd06114b16d8641e6a09cc74401d97c6","tid":352731,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"其實全家都同香港無關？"},{"pid":"6a14f7776823b79e38fd060bc694e5c3bfad2018","tid":352731,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"38c9b6255fb825405e122a98cf1c770000b622a5","tid":352731,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26c185cf4b0a954b31093866b3b851bbc02c2f7","tid":352731,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"&gt;☭新移民☭<br />\n<br />\n其實有無淨係睇 ☭新移民☭ 嘅香港犯罪數據？<br />\n如果有應該會同佔總人口百分比極度disproportionate"},{"pid":"c506e57bd3023bb4b4b59b357f4b62b7fe6550c6","tid":352731,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d8c21650c43f893325e57af660ab2122a6a35d7","tid":352731,"uid":47135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&gt;☭新移民☭<br />\n<br />\n其實有無淨係睇 ☭新移民☭ 嘅香港犯罪數據？<br />\n如果有應該會同佔總人口百分比極度disproportionate</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新移民犯罪問題嚴重"},{"pid":"14b1305a132b54db0f34a54ccc500a355ef23459","tid":352731,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86d859b380a5cbda75a1c7637905193b0d11a54c","tid":352731,"uid":65889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"「居所<span style=\"color: red;\">外</span>發現用過的安全套」，點解知係個姦夫？"},{"pid":"7a6ffcc19d2d6091052bd22217d7ca6c9b4f079d","tid":352731,"uid":65889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會係強國先有既牌子?<br />\n數住屋企仲有幾多個剩？"},{"pid":"062420f32a94f79a6e3e990cf462fa968d99b07b","tid":352731,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee79ac769020b1effb007fd653ee026f266ef628","tid":352731,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"仆街啦，我平時打完飛機會將個套掉係出面垃圾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e52a51447208f6c33bd46f88c92b98399e65eb3","tid":352731,"uid":62060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「居所<span style=\"color: red;\">外</span>發現用過的安全套」，點解知係個姦夫？</blockquote><br />\n味道是一樣的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實真正誘因係嬲個女人搶走佢小巴情人，因妒成恨"},{"pid":"7abcab6b62df414b183c22f54c284aef5de9ae5d","tid":352731,"uid":42925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"睇到相約做愛笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家新聞咁直接架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34fe5adcbe6d4165a4046890814caf48db56078","tid":352731,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到相約做愛笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家新聞咁直接架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}